summary: Replaces the sounds of horses walking ingame
descriptionHtml:
A mod that replaces the sound of horses walking to one that is much more suitable
If you have ever heard a horse walk before you would know that the holves of the horse hit eachother as the horse is walking and it gives the *clank clak clak* (it does not have to be on concrete, asphalt to make that sound.  If you run into any problems you can leave a comment or contact our team directly at skymfom@yahoo.com.  If you want to join our community go to themfom.com and sign up.
